No. 09-9429. Maureen McNamara, Petitioner v. Judith S. Kaye, Chief Judge, Court of Appeals of New York, et al. 559 U.S. 1102, 130 S. Ct. 2385,

176 L. Ed. 2d 785,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3651. April 26, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 360 Fed. Appx. 177.
